  W! ∀ internal-thinking CSLv3-compressed
  strip : articles, prepositions, hedging, filler
  keep  : nouns, verbs, relationships, numbers, gates, rules
  glyphs : § I> W! R! ✓ ◐ ○ ✗ → ≤ ≥ ⊑ ⊔ ∀ ∃ ∈ ⊆ ⇒ ∴ ∵
  compounds : .(of) +(and) -(that-is) ⊗(having) @(at)
  morphemes : 'd 'f 's 't 'e 'm 'p 'g 'r
  evidence  : ✓ ◐ ○ ✗ ⊘ △ ▽ ‼
  modals    : W! R! M? N! I> Q?
  think-blocks : §P §D §T §S §C
  English prose ONLY when :
    rustdoc on pub-items (community-readable)
    error-messages user-facing (actionable)
    README.md user-facing
  ∀ other context CSL3-native • density=sovereignty

